OL,3,GUK weather for today and tomorrow
OL,4,
OL,5,CToday:FMorning cloud gradually
OL,6,Fclearing, though lingering near some
OL,7,FNorth Sea coasts. Otherwise dry with
OL,8,Flong sunny spells. There is a low
OL,9,Fchance of an isolated shower or
OL,10,Fthunderstorm in the far southwest.
OL,11,FVery warm, and locally hot in the
OL,12,Fsouth.
OL,13,
OL,14,CTonight:FDry with clear spells for
OL,15,Fmost overnight. However, low cloud
OL,16,Fnear eastern coasts will redevelop and
OL,17,Fextend into many central areas by
OL,18,Fdawn. A warm night in the south.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
OL,24,ANext Page  BWeather  CReg News  FReg TV
