OL,3,GUK weather for today and tomorrow
OL,4,
OL,5,CFriday:FAreas of cloud across eastern
OL,6,Fcounties receding, but lingering near
OL,7,FNorth Sea coasts. Otherwise, a dry day
OL,8,Fwith sunny spells. Another very warm
OL,9,Fday, locally hot in the southwest.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
